Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.25,0:01:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了吗 我都等烦了 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那表情是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是忘记了这张脸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.76,0:02:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是银啊 姬你的老熟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.41,0:02:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为我被你这样挑衅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有要求的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.88,0:02:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到还有交涉的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这样明事理的町长真是太好了啊 苍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.19,0:02:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然想要参加一下祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.82,0:02:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能把那里打开一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿着钥匙对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神要去洞里？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.19,0:02:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面布满了『七乡』的芽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:41.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把妖力传送进去 让『七乡』开花
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.46,0:02:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 如果做了那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.58,0:02:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就只有让这家伙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被最喜欢的哥哥紧紧抱着身体
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为这样就可以得手吗？ 姬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.81,0:03:18.66,TITLE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,1000)}{\pos(480,335)}是时…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.35,0:03:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名 把苍带走…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『88(FLAK36 88毫米炮)』
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.68,0:03:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次不会让你跑掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好弱呐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多强的武器 终究只是言灵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要忘记还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 不用担心的 蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分的举动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你会为高兴的庆祝再会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.73,0:05:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会？怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 你没有说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见到过我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.75,0:05:31.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 秋名你…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 集中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.88,0:05:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.54,0:05:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 银的拳头的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不打死你 我保留了力量了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.98,0:06:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做的蛮有意思嘛 蓧塚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助去姬那里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对付这家伙我一个人就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄飞大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.16,0:06:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样惊慌到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.24,0:07:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 又弄脏了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.91,0:07:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然热衷工作不错 但这是很重要的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念波还真是便利的东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.47,0:07:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附带的『觉』的力量 连你的心都可以读懂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在犹豫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.55,0:07:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用枪对着这个身体 心情满是犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.68,0:07:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是害怕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.37,0:07:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要杀掉朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？谁是你的...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逞强也没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.67,0:07:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要用那双手伤害银
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.64,0:08:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是会犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名也在害怕着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是这么想的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那里别动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说中了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是円神
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『八彩』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那乱套的枪法是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『火消』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『云切』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的觉悟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有够可靠的呢 町长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『大花火』
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是萧索的烟花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.71,0:08:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭助 円神怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才那下砸的好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前面？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言叶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法完全变成妖怪的东西 是打不过我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.12,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在说那种话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝着变成妖怪 却用着妖怪的力量保护着城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事情充满矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说了吗 你那套我不懂的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.35,0:10:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『壁』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.55,0:10:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『矢』
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气息消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.05,0:10:32.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是伙伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉呢 能不能打开那里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.90,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去可不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.82,0:10:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雄飞大人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要出手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土地神可以做的顶多只是帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右城镇命运的事情不可出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会变成怎么样的呢 这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.04,0:11:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是火灾?哪啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是爆炸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想大概是神社的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.79,0:11:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华 姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.50,0:11:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们过去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那个世界现在变成怎样了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 原来不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.73,0:12:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是背负着那个使命吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.26,0:12:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你连把妖怪送往怎样的一个场所你都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.66,0:12:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在问你 知道还是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.68,0:12:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:30.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的世界啊 远远惨过人类界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所有 是被永恒的停滞所支配着的世界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:46.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于给人类添麻烦的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他们送往那个世界就再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.35,0:12:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.92,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果『七乡』之花盛开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个世界就能和这个世界连接上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.01,0:12:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界和那边的世界将会融为一体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与曾将我送去的那个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:04.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你们比泉家曾将我送去的那个世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好心当成驴肝肺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会被送归 是因为你根本就没有期待着和人类共存吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明人类自己就根本就没有期待着和妖怪共存
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.79,0:13:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何妖怪却需要这种期待
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本无心攻击 枪也变得迟钝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.05,0:13:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样脸的原因吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.84,0:13:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,困惑吗 迷茫吗 还是犹豫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.37,0:13:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…不是真正的银
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.79,0:13:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银依然在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在里面…在这具身体里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.37,0:14:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.95,0:14:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到这种地步了还残留着灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全部都不出手吗…对这具身体
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.19,0:14:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啊…试着把他打倒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要保护城镇的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想让那些樱花绽放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就试着让这具身体消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这个灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛快至极啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幼稚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋名…给我把它打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开它
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:15:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要赏花了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.23,0:16:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.82,0:16:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八重大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.70,0:16:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可要被罚的啊 八重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个臭土地神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…不能就这样空手而归
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚六爷子 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.04,0:17:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界被...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先拿下一城了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖力已经送够了…再也无法阻止了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,円神
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.79,0:18:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』…在绽放...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.34,0:18:30.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬  『七乡』…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.09,0:18:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果花绽放 被送归的妖怪将会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.17,0:18:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的平衡就会被打乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的一切都会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.85,0:19:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.11,0:19:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打算做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.60,0:19:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』...到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,『七乡』绽放的话 这个城镇也就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.66,0:19:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上代的町长是这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.08,0:20:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱花…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃华 在里面 京介在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？ 是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有…如此...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.14,0:23:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小铃 你有没有对未来的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.62,0:23:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有的是某一天独立
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.89,0:23:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且有一家自己的店
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.88,0:24:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店长也许会喜极而泣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店门弄不能没有特色想弄的时尚一点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面氛围充满着爵士乐曲的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.12,0:24:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家店一定很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.68,0:24:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更衣室？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.22,0:24:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集各种关于迷惑的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐…不开拉面店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.66,0:24:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我讨厌拉面
